enhanced_by.reason: The 'complete' method requires a parsed document to be present, which is set up by the 'parse' method.
The 'complete' method may be used after parsing a fragment, which is set up by the 'parseFragment' method.
Both 'complete' and 'completeFragment' methods finalize the parsing process and return a result, making them useful for constructing assertions.
The 'document' method provides the current parsed document, which can be used to assert the state of the document before and after calling 'complete'.
